name: Rêve impromptu
description:
I had a dream.

I don’t remember everything and some details are blurry in my memories. I was walking in Tokyo around Akihabara. The sky and colors were surrealist, I was feeling to be in an 80s anime. Waking up us always complicated after such a dream.

For this photograph I took in Japan, I wanted to give it a vaporwave aesthetic that I love with a purple sky, pink, blue colors and a dreamy vibe.

[Fine Art print for collector]
